title: Pete
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Pete (disambiguation)

Pete may refer to:

  • Makeover Mage, whose name is Pete when in male form
  • 'Picarron' Pete, a pirate aboard the Lady Zay
  • ScarFace Pete, a man from the Heroes' Quest
  • Dell Monti, called Pineapple Pete by his former crew
  • Solus Dellagar, a dangerous criminal nicknamed Stealthy Pete

Pete family[edit | edit source]

  • Parroty Pete, the parrot keeper at Zoo
  • Party Pete, who runs the Party Room
  • Pious Pete, a monk whom players assist in the Candlelight Random event
    • Pious Pete (20th Anniversary event), the return of this monk in the Realm of Memories
  • Pirate Pete, a pirate north of Port Phasmatys
  • Postie Pete, the postman of RuneScape
  • Prison Pete, a prisoner in his self-titled random event in ScapeRune

Names Pete is derived from[edit | edit source]

  • Peter
  • Peter (rabbit)
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
